dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset simulating realistic interactions across various applications commonly found with digital assistants, structured to encompass a diverse range of contexts representing different synthetic user activities and interactions.
dcterms:title: Implicit Query Dataset

dcterms:description: A toolbox containing APIs for various applications, generated using in-context learning with GPT-4, aimed at providing a comprehensive set of APIs that can perform actions on the applications considered.
dcterms:title: Synthetic Toolbox
